<br />Mr Iain Houston, an alumnus of the University and holder of the Postgraduate Certificate of Education from the Faculty of Education in 2004-05, beat very stiff competition to be awarded the accolade of Scottish Teacher of the Year at the 2009 Scottish Education Awards.</li>
<li title="home &gt; faculties &gt; Faculty of Education &gt; News and events &gt; Faculty events &gt; picturebooks">

<strong>SSLA Award for BEd4 Dissertation</strong>
<br />Congratulations to Nicola Kennedy who has been awarded the prize for joint runner up for the best final year dissertation, awarded by the Scottish Support for Learning Association. In addition to her prize Nicola’s dissertation will be published in the association’s journal. Commenting on her success Nicola said&nbsp; ‘I was very pleased to hear of my achievement and to know that the long hours spent in the university library were worthwhile.’<br /></li></ul></div>
